    thinking: "**Envisioning Elite Biology**\n\nI\'m now diving deep into this \"elite interactive biology experience\" concept, with xylem and phloem in mind. The markdown description is inspiring; it\'s practically a blueprint. My focus now is on translating this dream into a tangible plan for a fresh start on the project, focusing on the immersive aspects. I\'m prioritizing interactivity and intuitive design.\n\n\n**Assessing The Prompt\'s Intent**\n\nI\'ve just performed a skill check to assess the tools needed for this task. It seems like cloud SQL and Firebase aren\'t required here. I\'m considering the potential use of Gemini API for generating custom content, given the objective to create a top-tier interactive experience for plant tissues. The master prompt emphasizes an interactive web experience, making the Gemini API potentially relevant for providing explanations or summaries, or even generating new content.\n\n\n**Evaluating Workspace Context**\n\nI\'m now analyzing the workspace files and installed dependencies to assess what\'s already in place. The presence of `@google/genai` is promising, aligning with the Gemini API consideration. I\'ve ruled out several skill sets as irrelevant to this specific project, such as `github-import-migration`, `google-maps-platform`, and others. My attention has shifted to the `image-generation` skill, which might be useful, pending further evaluation based on the 3D emphasis.\n\n\n"
