    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/App.tsx` to tie together the guided story panel, the state-of-the-art visualizer, the cell explorer, the warning board, and the gamified quiz. This creates a fully reactive, polished, museum-grade applet that adapts from archival light to bioluminescent dark styles."
